      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 17:22:32 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Google Keep&amp;#39;s recent update offloaded reminders to Google Tasks, and it&amp;#39;s been such a massive downgrade because they constantly go out of sync. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;I loved Keep, but I&amp;#39;ll have to switch. What are people using these days to manage their todos?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
