      <link>https://androiddev.social/@saket/115606791505734042</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Nov 2025 21:27:25 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Jake and Jesse were my CN Tower. I only worked with them occasionally, but I always felt reassured just knowing they were around if I needed help. I&amp;#39;m mad our company lost both of them in the same week, and I&amp;#39;m afraid the entire Android OSS community is going to feel the ripple effect in the days to come.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
